schools.name: Dr Bryan C Jack Elementary School

data.description: Great South Tyler location off of Old Jacksonville Hwy close to Jack Elementary.  Don't wait to see this 4/2/2 with 1991 Sq Ft priced to sell!  This home was updated in 2017 to include hardwood floors, light fixtures, appliances.  Then further updated to included mini water heater under the sink for hot water, induction range, paint, roof (2023), custom curtains and blinds. This home has a HUGE living area with recessed lighting and a corner fireplace.  The large kitchen has granite tile countertops, island, pantry, updated sink and faucet with window to the backyard.  The house has a split floor plan arrangement.  The bedroom in the front would make an ideal study.  The master has wood floors, ceiling fan and large master bath with double sinks, walking in shower and large closet.  The yard has a 6ft privacy fence, sprinkler system, large covered back patio and a walkway on the side of the house.  This house would be the perfect place for you to call home!
